@startuml
title Manage Semesters Activity Diagram
|Admin|
start
:View Semester List;
|System|
:Display Semester List;
|Admin|
:Click "Add Semester";
|System|
:Display Add Form;
|Admin|
:Fill Details (Type, Dates, Year);
:Submit Form;
|System|
if (Validation?) then (Valid)
    :Create Semester Record;
    :Show Success Message;
else (Invalid)
    :Show Error Message;
    stop
endif

stop
@enduml
